{"tid":1863133,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【核彈！隔離營隨時變超級播菌集中營！】","createTime":"2020-02-05T04:14:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T13:02:39.000Z","uid":43204,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9eb6a1465859ccfe6d5b106b980e17520b265869","tid":1863133,"uid":43204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T04:14:58.000Z","msg":"係隔離營當值既姑娘有野想同大家講<br />\n<br />\n姑娘入營係要一齊入去住<br />\n間房就係懷疑染病、被隔離既病人附近<br />\n做野已經驚中招<br />\n休息訓覺都感受到個種壓迫感<br />\n<br />\n而且營入面既衞生又唔好<br />\n床單又有漬 又唔知有無消毒<br />\n完全得唔到充分休息<br />\n<br />\n我地原本係衛生署姑娘<br />\n入營第一日返9am-5pm<br />\n第二日就由2pm去到第三日既11am <br />\n足足係21個小時困係入面!!!! <br />\n<br />\n之後果日就要返clinic接觸公眾<br />\n係！你無聽錯<br />\n我地係直出番社區clinic<br />\n衞生署clinic包咩？<br />\n就係咩都有！普通市民又有<br />\n公務員診所又有<br />\n母嬰健康院都係衛生署！<br />\n好擔心自己做左超級病毒傳播員😭<br />\n<br />\n我幾辛苦都好 都一定會同大家打贏場瘟疫<br />\n林鄭呢條仆街真係想香港人攬炒<br />\n係手足既！同我share呢個消息出去！<br />\n大家出少d街 照顧好自己就幫到我地<br />\n<br />\n立即封關 罷工救港<br />\n康復香港 時代抗疫<br />\n<br />\n#手足投稿<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/c/1307213416/13596\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fc%2F1307213416%2F13596&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pcZE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=b999bc5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/c/1307213416/13596</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aqaB3Ge.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaqaB3Ge.jpg&h=bfe106e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GKV6GsV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGKV6GsV.jpg&h=1e16a0da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"077d89ce2354d73003d1d7ea47b228c035e412f4","tid":1863133,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T04:19:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba94ef1997372db6ea99752337d8b3755fa952a","tid":1863133,"uid":160294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T04:19:40.000Z","msg":"辛苦你地喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n撐醫護<br />\n就算疫爆都唔割！"},{"pid":"e1be22f013c443d796cf38d5f716e8eb1641c7ca","tid":1863133,"uid":283442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T04:21:00.000Z","msg":"推上報<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a7fadb4a016a991cdfbab8f145d7ec4dee4d89","tid":1863133,"uid":43204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T04:23:43.000Z","msg":"1/20"},{"pid":"4795e9db05f7c34ebd1c76ba78db76d9c46a7a18","tid":1863133,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T04:25:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dccb80d22205fd10fa206a50197bc24b5b66b80a","tid":1863133,"uid":250508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T04:26:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e2c46d7509729572e8f680beb52d3e8e24c75c9","tid":1863133,"uid":46333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T04:28:03.000Z","msg":"Cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddae3f1f59ec9eee341f152d54c2d10f3f4533c5","tid":1863133,"uid":43204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T04:28:42.000Z","msg":"2/20"},{"pid":"70e441f768e6cf25d5403eb217c94c754ef5083b","tid":1863133,"uid":160294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T04:30:00.000Z","msg":"推上報等記者問政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45f416d861c6989e5fc5f50303e1ad1065ebac5e","tid":1863133,"uid":61334,"like":0,"dis